column4: 'Does anyone need help with the homework?'
'Yes, I do. Can you explain problem 5?'
'Thanks for sharing! I''ll try it out.'
'Great idea! I suggest we go camping.'
'Here''s a playlist for you all to enjoy.'
'Thanks for sharing! I''ll listen to it.'
'I recommend this book for our next discussion.'
'I''m thinking of upgrading. Thanks for sharing!'
